@cindex tools

The @activity{Tools} activity is divided into 6 process:
@menu
* Syslog::       @process{Syslog}
* Apache::       @process{Apache}
* Exim::         @process{Exim}
* Ssh::          @process{Ssh}
* Cvs::          @process{Cvs}
* Cron::         @process{Cron}
@end menu

Flood diagram:

@image{mediatex-figures/tools,,,,}

@itemize @bullet
@item Events in
@table @code
@item @eventToolsSyslogMessage 
from @activityClient{}, @activityServer and @activityScripts to @procToolsSyslog{}: log @mediatexO operations.

@item @eventToolsApacheHttpGet 
@itemx @eventToolsApacheHttpPost 
@itemx @eventToolsApacheStartDownload
from @actorUser to @procToolsApache{}: @actorUserO's queries generated by its internet browser.

@item @eventToolsApacheReload
@itemx @eventToolsApacheRestart
from @procScriptsInitRemovePurge to @procToolsApache{}: re-configure @acronym{APACHE}.

@item @eventToolsEximSendMail 
from @procScriptsDeliver to @procToolsExim{}: archive availability notification.

@item @eventToolsSshCopy 
from @procClientMisc to @procToolsSsh{}: copy file from one remote server's cache.

@item @eventToolsCvsInit 
from @procScriptsInitRemovePurge to @procToolsCvs{}: initialise the local server's repository.

@item @eventToolsCvsImport
@itemx @eventToolsCvsCheckout
from @procScriptsInitRemovePurge or @procScriptsNewFreeClean to @procToolsCvs{}: respectively create or join a new collection.

@item @eventToolsCvsUpdate 
@itemx @eventToolsCvsCommit 
from @procScriptsUpdateCommit to @procToolsCvs{}: synchronise the meta-data.

@item @eventToolsCronDate
from @actorDate to @procToolsCron: scheduled tasks.

@end table
@item Processing

@pxref{How}

@item Events out
@table @code

@item @eventScriptsCgiGetQuery
@itemx @eventScriptsCgiPostQuery
from @procToolsApache to @procScriptsCgi{}: replies to the @actorUserO's internet browser.

@item @eventActorUserHtmlForm 
(if archive is not available) ...
@item @eventActorUserHtmlRedirect 
(if archive is available) @*
from @procToolsApache to @actorUserO

@item @eventActorUserMail 
from @procToolsExim to @actorUserO{}: archive availability notification.

@item @eventActorPublisherMail 
from @procToolsExim to @actorPublisherO{}: audit availability notification.

@item @eventActorAdminMail
from @procToolsExim to @actorAdminO{}: scheduled task error notification.

@item @eventScriptsCronHourly
@itemx @eventScriptsCronDaily
@itemx @eventScriptsCronMonthly
from @procToolsCron{} to @procScriptsCron: scheduled tasks.
@end table

@end itemize

